<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="1May1927"><font color="red">UPLund 1 May 1927</font> (to Eric Pinker): If you have not been able to secure American publication for the two pieces I sent you will you kindly return them to me? Is there any other way by which I can protect them? </div>
